    <item>
      <title>Paper is accepted in IEEE Design &amp; Test 2021</title>
      <link>https://diwu1990.github.io/post/ieeedt-accepted/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Dec 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://diwu1990.github.io/post/ieeedt-accepted/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This paper is titled &amp;ldquo;In-Stream Correlation-Based Division and Bit-Inserting Square Root in Stochastic Computing&amp;rdquo; in the IEEE Design &amp;amp; Test 2021 Special Issue on Stochastic Computing for Neuromorphic Architectures. And it is an extended version of the previous &lt;a href=&#34;https://diwu1990.github.io/publication/2019-06-02-dac/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;DAC&#39;19 paper&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
